Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有些寬過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:09.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正合身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的衣服也挺寬的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來已經準備好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今後就要正式工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我得先跟你說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來我店裡的客人全都是上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:29.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 或者說是如上帝般的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對客人要有禮貌 說話要用敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該說 是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:39.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,平時呢沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的時候也要跟我們用敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他媽 其它的你再教點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先就是服務客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就先看我做一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:55.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不做…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看我幹也在工作範圍內哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
