Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:19.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 這不是杏子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你怎麼來這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然是來吃飯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您想好要點什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是拉麵加炒飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回鍋肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來客人您很有錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在小看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拉麵加炒飯 還有回鍋肉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我說杏子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然她是這麼說 但是跟熟人可以隨便一點的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這傢伙就不是什麼上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是個普通人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你小看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你怎麼會在這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔阿姨收養了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那還挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:25.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛被收養就幹活 還挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛和她真是沒法比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能再想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你來做做收銀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟我剛才做的一樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然合計要1500元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你很快就會知道 這沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(737,0)\c&H8EE4EB&\3c&H52808B&\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs80\frz18.26\pos(1020,436)}錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子看到太多錢 人僵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子啊 洗得怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一次性筷子扔掉就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不都是洗洗再用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:32.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前茂叔教我這筷子洗洗就能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在杏子的心中活著很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我說過這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但感覺一直在不斷否定她的過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以後也要繼續幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作都結束了 就跟平常一樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 我放好洗澡水了你去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道該怎麼洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就是冷水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直都是在公園洗的 沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在可以用熱水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:24.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在可以隨便用電燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:31.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天還不太明白 原來這是我的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:33.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一個家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安叔 茂叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今後也會加…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:53.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.93,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(410,770)}超能力女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.98,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(487,900)\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1518,748)}超能力女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,提問 有「パン」但吃不了的「パン」是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}フライパン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除了「平底鍋」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「住一宿吃頓飯」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}一宿いっぱん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那還是吃了啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「鐵板」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「てっぱん」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有「安全褲」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(1018,998)}見せパン
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有熊貓也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}「パンダ」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 新田 新田！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上課總是睡覺 我今天一定饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是來學校幹什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為你老是這樣 考試也總不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說新田 你在認真聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這現在表情是什麼態度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我也不是想生氣才生氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:31.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是狠下心來才對你生氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畫出東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再多給我點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還要給其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:46.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,態度真差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,學校真是無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說想去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:57.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是無聊 就努力創造點樂趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近要舉行學生會成員競選了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想參加的人在下次參加課外活動的時候去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:06.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又流口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你這麼認真 考不考慮加入學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,紗夜你也挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看你還戴著眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在說笑話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會決定某些事情的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也制定一些新校規
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比如讓不讓看漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說這是學校裡的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掌權者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是學生會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說老大是學生會 倒不如說學生會長才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這說的也太隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係了 畢竟她是雛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,掌權者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老子終於獲得了權利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老子就是老大 規則都是老子來定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我居然沒辦法反抗權力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:00.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 有人想競選學生會成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有其他人了嗎 沒了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 新田競選學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說雛 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為學生會長 手握大權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪健吾你說了那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:35.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 在這之前 第一年只能當委員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還挺有趣的 靜觀其變怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:48.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下個星期學校早會上要發表演講
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該可以吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我教師生涯裡第一次聽這句話會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:03.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老師的班裡還有這麼積極參加競選的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他嗤笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 雛你在寫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,參加競選的人要進行演講
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我睡覺也沒人對我發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能多提供飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:24.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了
