Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:25.20,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz10.54\move(1389.333,762.667,1401.334,854.666,5,4926)}沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 你這不過是把想法羅列了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好寫演講原稿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你參加了學生會長的競選
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看來我應該是睡昏頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼來著 說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我參加了學生會長的競選
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是睡醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說一年級能當學生會長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的學校都是這麼幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:03.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別人說我的演講稿不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz18.75\pos(788,456)}希望我睡覺也沒人對我發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(728,570)\frz18.49}希望能多提供飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.93,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz20.75\pos(1069.333,640.667)}沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是荒唐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩死了 你自己考慮考慮唄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:16.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是新田說的努力創造點樂趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 事情變得比較麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:27.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這無論如何也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛她都已經這麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這廢什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你得盡力幫她啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 讓咱們的顧問律師來改改怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是組裡的人遇上條子找麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是這種程度的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 到底出什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還真叫來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:01.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來將進行學生會候選人的演講
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年三班 新田雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慘了 感覺好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:12.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底會變成怎麼樣的演講呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:23.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一年三班的新田雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我當選上學生會長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級生只能當書記或者會計的候選人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我當選上學生會長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}徹底無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我將努力改善伙食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我校的伙食在二十五年間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一直委託給朝香伙食中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是包括鄰近的學校在內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都與其簽訂了長年的協定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:55.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其內部情況 從成本、質量這兩個方面來看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實在也不能說是處於很好的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:02.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 以競爭投標的方式來選擇其他公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,致力於降低成本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}同時得以據此提高伙食的質量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在講很一本正經的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:14.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓學生對伙食感到安全性 還有營養這一方面也能有所改善吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讀到這裡深吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(860,602)\shad0\bord2\frz27.28\fn思源宋体 CN\b1\c&H535157&\3c&HFFFFFF&}讀到這裡深吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,深吸一口氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 比起伙食改善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:28.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飽餐一頓之後 無論如何都會變得暈暈欲睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前剛才那句話什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡舉起手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這不是沒舉起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓大家可以午後的打個小盹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:36.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}繼續讀下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,將會引入午睡時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 引入的方法是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺時不時會冒出點東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:47.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至於午睡的效果 請看接下來的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz31.73\c&H727272&\pos(698,758)}是否感到午覺有效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(632,692)\frz34.22}有效 79%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\frz30.55\pos(542,412)}沒感覺 21%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz30.53\c&H79787C&\bord2\pos(1140,586)}引入午睡制度後的成績變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:47.97,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz29.79\pos(846,188)\c&H000000&\bord2}引入前 引入後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看了這個之後想必大家就一目了然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 資料在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:58.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以上 我的演講完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡鞠個躬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:08.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然槽點有點多 不過真是了不起的演講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:12.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只是她說的完全超出了學生會的職能範圍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,600)\fn思源宋体 CN\shad0\bord1\c&H505052&\3c&HFFFFFF&}學生會成員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 這也是一開始就定好的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:30.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能成為學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,成了還得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行啦 今天就去外面吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼想吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鮭魚子蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛一次都沒去過學生會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 會長囑咐我今天必須把她帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你稍微來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你來就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想著這樣會比較容易看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快一點的話就趕不上開店了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡擺成這樣比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實效率提高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,關於運動會的請願書…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經整理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都沒來 我還想著發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是三島
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下來也能過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正新田她也不來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就當代理書記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到 學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:44.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,welcome……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:49.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐 下次跟我一起去吃頓飯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:53.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼辦好呢 我工作很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近不也沒什麼大事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不在店裡也沒差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是我的店哦 我在就很重要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的花瓶宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐完全不為所動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說又能怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟別人傾述一下會比較輕鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 怎麼說了句最不像你會說的話top10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,電視上說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我要跟雛商量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛話題？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有沒有自尊心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 新田先生他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是有邀請詩子小姐去約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但據說不順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是如果進展順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐可能會成為你媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來小雛的媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田他好像也有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 兩個人進展不順利的時候要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你問我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:15.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 戀愛什麼的還太早了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:19.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 到底是怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\an8}太平間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:25.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 那麼早就沒了媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我做不到什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會加油哦 會給你應援的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要若無其事地講些新田先生的好話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,儘可能地讓詩子小姐願意和他去約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:45.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小雛也一起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田說他想跟詩子你約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我們根本就沒達成共識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 派小孩來遊說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田還真是幹了件了有品的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著誤會 對新田先生的評價也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的哦 其實是小雛感受到了你們倆之間的氛圍之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 她感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 新田先生的優點！優點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田是個好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會給我做飯 什麼都會買給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種就是個好利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 去約會一次也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,工作上詩子小姐不在也完全不會困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去就行了吧！我去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:52.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}電視機前的乖孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田和美佳都是黑頭髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}義史8歲 美佳6歲 拿著蒼蠅拍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:58.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在學習媽媽相關知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:03.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為詩子會成為我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:06.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事這個神展開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她說願意和我約會了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主張做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上一直久攻不下也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為有孩子只會是我的減分點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 反而可以成為利器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好啊 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到約會的時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我要留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說這次都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:05.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 明明你都住院了我卻一個人去享受也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也想要媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:23.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著 下次再見的時候媽媽也會一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實收到了 你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我已經給你看過我哭的醜態了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:37.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是直到能與媽媽相見那時為止 你可先別讓我看你的哭臉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那時的眼淚 一定是喜悅的眼淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我是個混黑道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:48.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會讓你和詩子小姐 笑容滿溢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搭建一個溫暖的家庭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我哦雛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,男子漢新田義史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此處 一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 拒絕他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:32.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上小雛也黏他黏得很緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的新田也光在講雛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓人覺得根本無法進入這兩人其中啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跟他說了離過一次婚還帶著孩子的男人不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這說法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的話還是說清楚比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:50.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,該說是清楚呢還是決絕呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:00.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 我是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:04.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 久等啦 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:06.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 笑一個
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
